{META_DATA}: (undeterred)
{DIALOGUE}: I'm going to be a fucking pariah.
{DIALOGUE}: Everyone's just going to be holding their breath to see if I'm going to get drunk and make a scene.
{DIALOGUE}: Plus Tony fucking Levin?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: No, no, no.
{DIALOGUE}: It's cool.
{DIALOGUE}: I talked to Victoria.
{DIALOGUE}: She's cool.
{DIALOGUE}: Everyone's cool.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MILES
{META_DATA}: (horrified)
{DIALOGUE}: You've all been talking about it?
{DIALOGUE}: Behind my back?
{DIALOGUE}: Talking about it?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Miles turns and locates an open BOTTLE of wine in the back seat.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He uncorks it and begins to swig.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: Hey, hey, hey.
{DIALOGUE}: No, you don't!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jack tries unsuccessfully to grab the bottle from Miles, but Miles bolts out of the car.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A VERY WIDE SHOT --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Pursued by Jack, Miles dashes down the hill, all the while taking huge swigs from the bottle.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OMIT.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. LOVELY VINEYARD - CONTINUOUS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Miles slows to walk between rows of GRAPEVINES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He polishes off the bottle and tosses it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A painting Jack catches up with him in the adjacent grapevine corridor.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Miles's face crumbles as though he were about to cry.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then he collapses to the ground and closes his eyes tight.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jack looks around impatiently for a moment.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then he squats down so he can see Miles underneath the vines.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
