{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Miles ignores Jack and focuses on the beautiful RIPE GRAPES that surround him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They seem to distract him from his pain.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JACK
{DIALOGUE}: You going to be okay?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Miles looks up and shakes his head a definitive NO.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jack can't help but LAUGH.
{META_DATA}: DISSOLVE TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. KALYRA WINERY PARKING LOT - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The sun hangs low as the Saab pulls into the parking lot, Jack at the wheel.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. KALYRA TASTING ROOM - DAY
