{CHARACTER_NAME}: VICTORIA (ON THE PHONE)
{DIALOGUE}: I'm going to hang up now, Miles.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MILES
{META_DATA}: (rushing to keep her on)
{DIALOGUE}: You see, Vicki, I just heard about this today, you getting married that is, and I was kind of taken aback.
{DIALOGUE}: Kind of hard to believe.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Silence.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MILES
{DIALOGUE}: I guess I just thought there was still some hope for us somewhere down the road and I just, I just --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VICTORIA (ON THE PHONE)
