{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then he takes a deep breath and drops his hands.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MILES
{DIALOGUE}: You are such a loser.
{DIALOGUE}: Come on!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. THE LIVING ROOM - NIGHT
