{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Amid turbulent water, Miles corrects his students' papers.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He is alone in the tub, but at the nearby pool STOCKY KIDS play noisily with SUPER-SOAKERS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OVER MILES'S SHOULDER --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The PAPER he's reading is marked up with circled spelling errors, and one entire paragraph has been crossed out.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Finding a new error, Miles writes "NO!!!"
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CAMERA PANS to reveal a STACK of papers already heavily marked with corrections, some of them mottled with water stains.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. MOTEL ROOM - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Miles FLOSSES, his lips pulled back into a grotesque moue.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Then he brushes with a SONIC-CARE TOOTHBRUSH.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: LATER --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Miles checks his machine.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SYNTHESIZED VOICE (O.S.)
{DIALOGUE}: No new messages.
