{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON A WATER-SAVER SHOWER HEAD --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: as little needles of water come at us.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: THROUGH THE BATHROOM DOOR --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Miles takes a nice hot SHOWER.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: But wait -- he has forgotten to put the shower curtain inside the tub.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A closer look reveals a growing PUDDLE OF WATER on the floor.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. THE HITCHING POST - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Miles walks across the parking lot.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He pauses before entering, then forces himself to take the leap.
